Package: SveltePlots
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Title: A Wrapper for a Svelte Custom Web Component
Authors@R: 
  person("Pascal", "Schmidt", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "pascal.sfu@gmail.com")
Author: Pascal Schmidt [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Pascal Schmidt <pascal.sfu@gmail.com>
Description: SveltePlots is an interactive charting library which aims to easily produce SVG charts. 
  In addition to that is was developed to remove renderUI, insertUI, removeUI, and proxy function through Svelte's excellent state management. 
